LEFT MARGIN
start button to open app viewer
workspace number (to enable easy switching)
app list (to show running app icons)

MIDDLE MARGIN
window name
... button to either (close, float/unfloat, pivot ) #optional

RIGHT MARGIN
volume (opens rofi applet for control)
wifi status (shows wifi and opens rofi panel on click)
clock (shows calendar on clicking, and displays the time in: Day, DayNumber, Time in 12 hr format)
menu button to open menu for quick system settings, wifi, time, notifications, etc

